* Fixed the bug that there was no prompt when verifying the fingerprint password;
* Fixed the bug that the keyboard layout was not shown completely in login screen;
* Fixed the abnormal display on login and lock screen under HiDPI;
* Fixed the display error of login, lock and shutdown screen under multiple screens;
* Fixed the driver issue for AMD graphics card;
* Fixed the bug that the mouse buttons cannot used to forward and backward in browser after switching on Mouse Acceleration;
* Fixed the bug that the logout music was still played after mute;
* Removed fireworkx and whirlwindwarp screensaver that have high CPU occupation;
Dock:
* Added the tray area visible at all times even the tray icons were folded;
* Fixed dock crash when switching dock mode after disabling the wired network card;
* Fixed the bug that some tray icons did not have any responses;
* Fixed the bug that there was no dock menu when right click around the tray icons in efficient mode;
